			<a class="AuthorLink" href="/user.asp?usr=28554">MochaBoy</a>&nbsp;<img src=/images/star.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="525 posts"><img src=/images/star.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="525 posts"><img src=/images/star.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="525 posts">&nbsp;			
